Error: Sorry, This File Type Is Not Permitted for Security Reasons (wordpress upload/media)
Solution:
1. Go to /public_html/wp-systcon/wp-config.php
2. You can add the following code to the file, anywhere above the line reading “/* That’s all, stop editing. Happy blogging. */”:
3. define('ALLOW_UNFILTERED_UPLOADS', true);
4. Done.
